@startuml
!theme materia-outline

title REQ_IVI_012: UDS 0x14 - Clear DTC (ASIL-B)

actor "Diagnostic Tester\n(CANoe)" as Tester
participant "CAN Bus" as CAN
box "vECU (Target)" #f9f9f9
    participant "DCM\n(Diagnostic Communication Manager)" as DCM
    participant "DEM\n(Diagnostic Event Manager)" as DEM
    participant "NvM\n(Non-volatile Memory)" as NVM
end box

== Extended Diagnostic Session ==

Tester -> CAN : 0x10 03\n(Extended Diagnostic Session)
activate CAN
CAN -> DCM : Session Request
activate DCM
DCM -> DCM : Validate Session Request
DCM --> CAN : 0x50 03\n(Positive Response)
CAN --> Tester : Session Active
deactivate DCM
deactivate CAN

note right of DCM
    **Session Established**
    • Extended Diagnostic Mode
    • Security Access Required
end note

== Clear DTC Request ==

Tester -> CAN : 0x14 FF FF FF\n(Clear All DTCs)
activate CAN
note right: REQ_IVI_012\nSuccess Rate: >99%

CAN -> DCM : Clear DTC Service
activate DCM

DCM -> DEM : Request Clear All DTCs
activate DEM

DEM -> DEM : Validate Request\n(Check Session State)

alt Clear DTC Successful
    DEM -> NVM : Erase DTC Storage
    activate NVM
    NVM -> NVM : Clear Flash Memory\n(DTC Area: 0x8000-0x8FFF)
    NVM --> DEM : Erase Complete
    deactivate NVM

    DEM -> DEM : Reset DTC Counters\nReset Freeze Frames
    DEM --> DCM : Clear Successful
    deactivate DEM

    DCM --> CAN : 0x54\n(Positive Response)
    CAN --> Tester : DTCs Cleared
    deactivate DCM
    deactivate CAN

else Clear DTC Failed
    DEM --> DCM : Clear Failed\n(Memory Error)
    deactivate DEM

    DCM --> CAN : 0x7F 14 22\n(Conditions Not Correct)
    CAN --> Tester : Clear Failed
    deactivate DCM
    deactivate CAN
end

== Verification ==

Tester -> CAN : 0x19 02 FF\n(Read DTC by Status Mask)
CAN -> DCM : Read DTC Request
activate DCM
DCM -> DEM : Get Stored DTCs
activate DEM
DEM --> DCM : No DTCs Found
deactivate DEM
DCM --> CAN : 0x59 02\n(No DTC Available)
CAN --> Tester : Verification Complete
deactivate DCM

note over Tester
    **REQ_IVI_012 Verified**
    • All DTCs cleared
    • Re-query returns empty
    • Success rate: >99%
end note

@enduml
